        "created_at": "2020-01-08T01:32:36.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Had many of his 2017s in barrel a year and a half ago, but they were hard to taste, although they seemed long and promising.  Cannot wait to taste more at the Paulee in NY in March.</p>",
