        "created_at": "2020-01-08T02:12:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"3\" data-topic=\"157400\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>Had many of his 2017s in barrel a year and a half ago, but they were hard to taste, although they seemed long and promising.  Cannot wait to taste more at the Paulee in NY in March.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>His malos are normally quite late so can be hard to taste early, I try to go towards the end of my time in Burgundy each year. You are in for a treat at La Paul\u00e9e.</p>",
